<article id="post-5613" class="post-5613 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-uncategorized">
			<header class="entry-header">
			<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="https://library.ryerson.ca/asc/2016/03/first-edition-book-award-2016-award-winners/">First Edition Book Award 2016 Award Winners</a></h1>
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->
	
	<div class="entry-content">

				<div class="entry-meta">
			<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="https://library.ryerson.ca/asc/2016/03/first-edition-book-award-2016-award-winners/" title="10:51 am" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2016-03-01T10:51:21-05:00" pubdate>March 1, 2016</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="https://library.ryerson.ca/asc/author/askyrme/" title="View all posts by Alison" rel="author">Alison</a></span></span>		</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
		
		
<p class="has-text-align-center">The Photography Studies program at Ryerson University&nbsp;together with Ryerson Archives &amp; Special Collections is pleased to&nbsp;announce the 2016 recipients:</p>



<h2 class="has-text-align-center">THE 2016 FIRST EDITION PHOTOBOOK AWARD</h2>



<h3 class="has-text-align-center">Book Award Recipients</h3>



<p class="has-text-align-center">Andrea Chartrand<br>Kaya Kelley<br>Mina Markovic<br>Terence Reeves<br>Gabriel Steele<br>Alia Youssef</p>



<h3 class="has-text-align-center">Honourable Mentions</h3>



<p class="has-text-align-center">Jeffrey Christenson<br>Kelsey Danahy<br>Alexandra Demelo<br>Sophie Trecroce</p>



<hr class="wp-block-separator"/>



