	</div><!-- .entry-content -->
	
</article><!-- #post-5524 -->
<hr class="post-separator" aria-hidden="true" />
<article id="post-5510" class="post-5510 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-uncategorized">
			<header class="entry-header">
			<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="https://library.ryerson.ca/asc/2015/12/happy-holidays-from-ryerson-library-archives-and-special-collections/">Happy Holidays from Ryerson Library Archives and Special Collections</a></h1>
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->
	
	<div class="entry-content">

				<div class="entry-meta">
			<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="https://library.ryerson.ca/asc/2015/12/happy-holidays-from-ryerson-library-archives-and-special-collections/" title="11:29 am" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2015-12-07T11:29:48-05:00" pubdate>December 7, 2015</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="https://library.ryerson.ca/asc/author/askyrme/" title="View all posts by Alison" rel="author">Alison</a></span></span>		</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
		
		
<p>As the Holiday season approachs, Ryerson students are making their final mighty push to get assignments done and exams written before the winter break.</p>



<p>Featured from our collections are some Holiday and Winter scenes from around campus and beyond for a little light viewing during this busy time of year.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter is-resized"><a href="http://library.ryerson.ca/asc/2014/12/happy-holidays-from-the-ryerson-university-archives-and-special-collections/rg395_121_01_08wm/" rel="attachment wp-att-4378"><img data-attachment-id="4378" data-permalink="https://library.ryerson.ca/asc/2014/12/happy-holidays-from-the-ryerson-university-archives-and-special-collections/rg395_121_01_08wm/" data-orig-file="https://library.ryerson.ca/asc/files/2014/12/RG395_121_01_08WM.jpg" data-orig-size="925,625" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-image-title="RG395_121_01_08WM" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://library.ryerson.ca/asc/files/2014/12/RG395_121_01_08WM-300x202.jpg" data-large-file="https://library.ryerson.ca/asc/files/2014/12/RG395_121_01_08WM-600x405.jpg" loading="lazy" src="http://library.ryerson.ca/asc/files/2014/12/RG395_121_01_08WM-600x405.jpg" alt="RG395_121_01_08WM" class="wp-image-4378" width="707" height="477" srcset="https://library.ryerson.ca/asc/files/2014/12/RG395_121_01_08WM-600x405.jpg 600w, https://library.ryerson.ca/asc/files/2014/12/RG395_121_01_08WM-150x101.jpg 150w, https://library.ryerson.ca/asc/files/2014/12/RG395_121_01_08WM-300x202.jpg 300w, https://library.ryerson.ca/asc/files/2014/12/RG395_121_01_08WM.jpg 925w" sizes="(max-width: 707px) 100vw, 707px" /></a><figcaption>Quadrangle in the Snow (<a href="https://archives.library.ryerson.ca/index.php/winter-scenes-2" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">RG 395.121.01.216</a>)</figcaption></figure></div>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter is-resized"><a href="http://library.ryerson.ca/asc/2015/12/happy-holidays-from-ryerson-library-archives-and-special-collections/rg95_1_41_53_01-3/" rel="attachment wp-att-5512"><img data-attachment-id="5512" data-permalink="https://library.ryerson.ca/asc/2015/12/happy-holidays-from-ryerson-library-archives-and-special-collections/rg95_1_41_53_01-3/" data-orig-file="https://library.ryerson.ca/asc/files/2015/11/RG95_1_41_53_01.jpg" data-orig-size="333,266" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}" data-image-title="Broomball" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://library.ryerson.ca/asc/files/2015/11/RG95_1_41_53_01-300x240.jpg" data-large-file="https://library.ryerson.ca/asc/files/2015/11/RG95_1_41_53_01.jpg" loading="lazy" src="http://library.ryerson.ca/asc/files/2015/11/RG95_1_41_53_01.jpg" alt="Black and white photograph of young men and women playing a hockey style game with brooms on an ice rink " class="wp-image-5512" width="704" height="562" srcset="https://library.ryerson.ca/asc/files/2015/11/RG95_1_41_53_01.jpg 333w, https://library.ryerson.ca/asc/files/2015/11/RG95_1_41_53_01-150x120.jpg 150w, https://library.ryerson.ca/asc/files/2015/11/RG95_1_41_53_01-300x240.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 704px) 100vw, 704px" /></a><figcaption>Howard Kerr Hall, ca. 1965, decorated for the holidays. (RG 95.1.41.53.01)</figcaption></figure></div>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter is-resized"><a href="http://library.ryerson.ca/asc/2015/12/happy-holidays-from-ryerson-library-archives-and-special-collections/1969_winter_carnival044/" rel="attachment wp-att-5513"><img data-attachment-id="5513" data-permalink="https://library.ryerson.ca/asc/2015/12/happy-holidays-from-ryerson-library-archives-and-special-collections/1969_winter_carnival044/" data-orig-file="https://library.ryerson.ca/asc/files/2015/11/1969_Winter_Carnival044.jpg" data-orig-size="2730,1501" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}" data-image-title="1969_Winter_Carnival044" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://library.ryerson.ca/asc/files/2015/11/1969_Winter_Carnival044-300x165.jpg" data-large-file="https://library.ryerson.ca/asc/files/2015/11/1969_Winter_Carnival044-600x330.jpg" loading="lazy" src="http://library.ryerson.ca/asc/files/2015/11/1969_Winter_Carnival044-600x330.jpg" alt="3 storey academic building at night with red, green and white twinkle lights decorating the outside" class="wp-image-5513" width="697" height="383" srcset="https://library.ryerson.ca/asc/files/2015/11/1969_Winter_Carnival044-600x330.jpg 600w, https://library.ryerson.ca/asc/files/2015/11/1969_Winter_Carnival044-150x82.jpg 150w, https://library.ryerson.ca/asc/files/2015/11/1969_Winter_Carnival044-300x165.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 697px) 100vw, 697px" /></a><figcaption>Ryerson Students participating in a massive broomball tournament in the Quad. Tournament was part of Ryerson&#8217;s Winter Carnival held in January 1969. Part of the Quad was turned into the ice rink. (RG 95.1.41.53.01)</figcaption></figure></div>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter is-resized"><a href="http://library.ryerson.ca/asc/2015/12/happy-holidays-from-ryerson-library-archives-and-special-collections/2009_002_2883_004/" rel="attachment wp-att-5515"><img data-attachment-id="5515" data-permalink="https://library.ryerson.ca/asc/2015/12/happy-holidays-from-ryerson-library-archives-and-special-collections/2009_002_2883_004/" data-orig-file="https://library.ryerson.ca/asc/files/2015/11/2009_002_2883_004.jpg" data-orig-size="591,393" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}" data-image-title="Country homes in winter" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://library.ryerson.ca/asc/files/2015/11/2009_002_2883_004-300x199.jpg" data-large-file="https://library.ryerson.ca/asc/files/2015/11/2009_002_2883_004.jpg" loading="lazy" src="http://library.ryerson.ca/asc/files/2015/11/2009_002_2883_004.jpg" alt="(2009.002.2883.004)" class="wp-image-5515" width="655" height="436" srcset="https://library.ryerson.ca/asc/files/2015/11/2009_002_2883_004.jpg 591w, https://library.ryerson.ca/asc/files/2015/11/2009_002_2883_004-150x100.jpg 150w, https://library.ryerson.ca/asc/files/2015/11/2009_002_2883_004-300x199.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 655px) 100vw, 655px" /></a><figcaption>Canadian Architect photograph file &#8220;Country Homes in Winter&#8221; (<a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://archives.library.ryerson.ca/index.php/country-homes-in-winter" target="_blank">2009.002.2883.004</a>)</figcaption></figure></div>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter is-resized"><a href="http://library.ryerson.ca/asc/2014/12/happy-holidays-from-the-ryerson-university-archives-and-special-collections/1950s/" rel="attachment wp-att-4389"><img data-attachment-id="4389" data-permalink="https://library.ryerson.ca/asc/2014/12/happy-holidays-from-the-ryerson-university-archives-and-special-collections/1950s/" data-orig-file="https://library.ryerson.ca/asc/files/2014/12/1950s.jpg" data-orig-size="1275,1650" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-image-title="1950s" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://library.ryerson.ca/asc/files/2014/12/1950s-231x300.jpg" data-large-file="https://library.ryerson.ca/asc/files/2014/12/1950s-463x600.jpg" loading="lazy" src="http://library.ryerson.ca/asc/files/2014/12/1950s-463x600.jpg" alt="1950s" class="wp-image-4389" width="632" height="819" srcset="https://library.ryerson.ca/asc/files/2014/12/1950s-463x600.jpg 463w, https://library.ryerson.ca/asc/files/2014/12/1950s-115x150.jpg 115w, https://library.ryerson.ca/asc/files/2014/12/1950s-231x300.jpg 231w, https://library.ryerson.ca/asc/files/2014/12/1950s.jpg 1275w" sizes="(max-width: 632px) 100vw, 632px" /></a><figcaption>Holiday Card from the 1950s.</figcaption></figure></div>



